node.text:
My heart is still shattered in a million pieces. The reality that Stache being gone is so unbearable at times. I cry so hard at night I can’t even breathe. I’ve changed so much emotionally since his departure. I’m more anxious, startle easily and worst of all I’m always a thought or two away from totally breaking down. I’m not a person who loves easily. But it comes so natural to me towards my cats. Maybe because they love me back unconditionally. I just know the hole in my heart is so big right now.  Lost without Stache. I want to go back when he wasn’t sick, when he was full of energy and life. Is it wrong for me to wear my emotions on my sleeve? I just don’t know anymore as I wade in this pool of sorrow without him. 

#hobbikats #memories #myheart #mylove #missyou
